{"tid":2206442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 將發行首張日語正規專輯！繽紛概念照大放送","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T13:10:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"645fc189d07c5cbe2f39629a2a4c5860b0a44529","tid":2206442,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"才剛舉行完線上演唱會，IZ*ONE 又帶來新的好消息，期待她們時隔一年的日語新專輯！<br />\n<br />\nOff the Record 最近陸續公開了 IZ*ONE 為首張日語正規專輯〈Twelve〉拍攝的各種畫報，彷彿糖果般的繽紛鮮豔的色彩顯得無比夢幻。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 於 2019 年初在日本正式出道，至今已發行過〈想讓你說喜歡我〉、〈Beunos Aires〉和〈Vampire〉三張單曲，和韓國活動風格截然不同的面貌經常讓各國粉絲為之驚艷。<br />\n<br />\n收錄 11 首歌的〈Twelve〉將於 10 月 21 日發行，在這同時，IZ*ONE 的首場演唱會《IZ*ONE 1 ST CONCERT [EYES ON ME]》相關 DVD / BLU-RAY / KIT VIDEO 也已經開放預購，想收藏的 WIZ*ONE 別忘了及時下單囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：Off the Record）"},{"pid":"5ec90201a842b30d7f12478da225ca75bdd1111c","tid":2206442,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_42a65b0f0d4c9f3a143a1914da285833/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130158-874124.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_42a65b0f0d4c9f3a143a1914da285833%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130158-874124.png&h=99d8f1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e0b10c183c6ce9f25fdfc12c5c6f68ae/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130158-874127.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e0b10c183c6ce9f25fdfc12c5c6f68ae%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130158-874127.png&h=f6272abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6a2059db33b70736ef684d570cee12f0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130158-874129.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6a2059db33b70736ef684d570cee12f0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-